## Application Description

Family Meal Planner is an application designed to help busy families organize their weekly meals. The application allows users to create meal plans, save recipes, prepare grocery lists, and keep track of meals for each day of the week.

## Problem the Application Solves

Many families struggle to decide what to cook each day and often spend too much money on last-minute meals. Family Meal Planner solves this problem by helping users plan meals in advance and create organized grocery lists.

## Target Users

The target users for this application are:

- Busy parents
- Families with children
- College students
- People who want to save money on food

## Key Features

The application will include the following features:

- Create weekly meal plans
- Add and save recipes
- Generate grocery lists
- Organize meals by breakfast, lunch, and dinner
- Edit or delete saved meals

## How the Application Works

Users will open the application and select a day of the week. They will choose or enter a meal for breakfast, lunch, or dinner. The application will save the meal and add the necessary ingredients to a grocery list.

Users can review their complete weekly plan, update meals, delete meals, and view their grocery list before shopping.
